{"tid":2118605,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】一班至少20人短則上課數小時 黨鐵堅持職員上培訓班","createTime":"2020-07-21T14:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T14:54:01.000Z","uid":220798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eb3ec0c9bbc528cfb5dcf83c9e675f7916eebd17","tid":2118605,"uid":220798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"港鐵職員Kay（化名）亦提到，近日上3小時培訓課程，一班大約20人，導師要求他們隔位坐。她表示，每日課室都有多人使用，不時出現「班接班」情況，但她未見有清潔工在下課後立即到課室進行清潔。她表示，將會到九龍灣車廠參與訓練課程，然而近日該車廠有外判商職員確診肺炎，故她向上司查詢會否延期時，上司則指會照常進行。她坦言感憂慮，直言未必了解一同上課的同事身體情況，並指即使要考核，仍尚餘數個月時間，「有空間去延遲課堂」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200721/R7GHVGHMFJFDQQMJYGAI6NBBKE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200721%2FR7GHVGHMFJFDQQMJYGAI6NBBKE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj4pVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=06a627a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200721%2FR7GHVGHMFJFDQQMJYGAI6NBBKE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=d6f4a062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200721/R7GHVGHMFJFDQQMJYGAI6NBBKE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n黨鐵真係日日都有新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日仲咁多人搭黨鐵，一個唔小心啲職員大爆發就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b839494dafb89ab3fb27cb68ad93c1f9c9fe796a","tid":2118605,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:54:01.000Z","msg":"爆到入青衣OCC就可以無人鴐駛"}]}